  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/14/flappy-bird-multiplayer/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/cfe852d8eb937f8bf4ee3ba7b841bb43/flappy-bird-returns-2014-02-04-01.jpg\" style=\"height: 412px; width: 620px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n许多<s>自虐狂魔</s>坚强玩家期待已久的《<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/flappybird\">Flappy Bird</a>》终于确定要在八月重回 App Store 了，虽然开发者 Dong Nguyen 之前已经透露过<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/19/flappy-bird-returns/\">这方面的想法</a>，但在日前接受 CNBC 采访时，他才首度松口介绍了一些新版本的细节。<br />\n<br />\n据称这次的作品将不会像过去那样容易让人上瘾，它可以让多个玩家同时参与，而且会有多种全新的游戏模式供大家选择（比如说让一个人在楼宇间跳来跳去等）。更多的消息还有待公布，好不容易让手指歇了几个月，这下又要忙活啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/14/flappy-bird-multiplayer/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/flappy-bird-will-return-as-a-multi-player-game-2014-5\" target=\"_blank\">Business Insider</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CNBCSocial/status/466681901101899776\" target=\"_blank\">CNBC (Twitter)</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/Kelly_Evans/status/466682487343939584\" target=\"_blank\">@Kelly_Evans</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/DonnaBurton/status/466681594934480896\" target=\"_blank\">@DonnaBurton</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/14/flappy-bird-multiplayer/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20886061/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/14/flappy-bird-multiplayer/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr siz